---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const techStack = ['Next.js', 'Tailwind CSS', 'MongoDB', 'Node.js', 'Express.js'];

const features = [
  'User authentication and profile management',
  'Structured course content with lessons',
  'Interactive mock tests with instant feedback',
  'Progress tracking and performance analytics',
  'Responsive design for mobile and desktop',
];

const meta = [
  { label: 'Role', value: 'Full Stack Developer' },
  { label: 'Status', value: 'Live in production' },
  { label: 'Stack', value: 'Next.js · MongoDB · Node' },
];
---

<PageLayout
  title="The SRS Classes — Awadh Kishor Singh"
  description="Case study of The SRS Classes, an educational platform for competitive exams."
  ogImage="https://picsum.photos/1200/630?random=4"
>
  <article class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:px-8 md:py-24">
    <a
      href="/projects"
      class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-mono text-xs text-[var(--muted)] transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-[var(--accent)]"
    >
      ← Back to projects
    </a>

    <span class="eyebrow">Case study</span>
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--fg)] md:text-5xl">
      The SRS Classes
    </h1>
    <p class="mb-10 max-w-[680px] text-base text-[var(--muted)] md:text-lg">
      An ed-tech platform helping aspirants prepare for BPSC and other competitive exams — courses,
      mock tests, and progress tracking in one polished interface.
    </p>

    <div class="mb-10 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[rgba(253,246,238,0.55)] backdrop-blur-[20px] dark:bg-[rgba(4,8,15,0.55)]">
      <img
        src="https://picsum.photos/800/400?random=4"
        alt="The SRS Classes"
        class="h-72 w-full object-cover md:h-96"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="mb-12 grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
      {meta.map((m) => (
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[rgba(253,246,238,0.55)] p-5 backdrop-blur-[20px] dark:bg-[rgba(4,8,15,0.55)]">
          <span class="font-mono text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--muted)]">{m.label}</span>
          <p class="mt-1.5 mb-0 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--fg)]">{m.value}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 mt-0 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--fg)]">Overview</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg)]">
          The SRS Classes is a comprehensive online learning platform that consolidates structured
          courses, study materials, and mock tests for competitive exam preparation. Built with a
          modern stack to keep the learning experience seamless across devices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 mt-0 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--fg)]">Problem</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg)]">
          Competitive exam aspirants were stitching together fragmented tools — separate places for
          notes, tests, and progress. Existing platforms felt clunky, and none of them put a
          coherent learning loop in one place.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 mt-0 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--fg)]">Solution</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg)]">
          A full-stack web app that brings courses, materials, mock tests, and analytics under one
          roof. Authentication, course management, and detailed performance tracking are all built
          to feel like a single product, not a stack of features.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-4 mt-0 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--fg)]">Tech stack</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {techStack.map((t) => (
            <span class="rounded-md border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)]/60 px-3 py-1.5 font-mono text-xs text-[var(--fg)]">
              {t}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-4 mt-0 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--fg)]">Key features</h2>
        <ul class="m-0 grid list-none gap-2 p-0 md:grid-cols-2">
          {features.map((f) => (
            <li class="m-0 flex items-start gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[rgba(253,246,238,0.55)] p-4 text-sm text-[var(--fg)] backdrop-blur-[20px] dark:bg-[rgba(4,8,15,0.55)]">
              <span class="mt-1.5 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)]"></span>
              <span>{f}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 mt-0 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--fg)]">Outcome</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-relaxed text-[var(--fg)]">
          The platform has launched and is now used by hundreds of aspirants in their exam
          preparation journey. It continues to be maintained and improved based on user feedback.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-3 border-t border-[var(--border)] pt-8">
      <a
        href="https://thesrsclasses.com"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-[var(--accent)] bg-[var(--accent)] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--bg)] transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[var(--accent-light)] hover:border-[var(--accent-light)]"
      >
        Visit live site →
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/imawadh/srs-website"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-transparent px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--fg)] transition-colors duration-300 hover:border-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--accent)]"
      >
        View code
      </a>
      <a
        href="/projects"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-transparent px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--fg)] transition-colors duration-300 hover:border-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--accent)]"
      >
        ← All projects
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</PageLayout>
